<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" 
	      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">
		  
<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Appearance 
</Paragraph> 


<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">The following samples are included under this category which illustrates the Appearance of the OlapGrid:</Paragraph>

<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Appearance Demo</Bold> - Demonstrates the various properties used to customize the appearance of an OlapGrid</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Frozen Header Demo</Bold> - Enables freezing row and column headers</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Hyperlink Cell Demo</Bold> - Enables hyperlink functionality in Cells</Paragraph>	
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Visual Styles Demo</Bold> - Demonstrates the various skin styles used for an OlapGrid</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Conditional Formatting Demo</Bold> - Demonstrates the cell of the OlapGrid will shows with some formats</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Cell Template Demo</Bold> - Demonstrates cell template  feature in OlapGrid</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Grid Layout Demo</Bold> -This sample illustrates how to show different grid layouts that are available in the OlapGrid control. The following layouts are available:</Paragraph>
<List>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"><Run FontWeight="Bold">Normal Grid Layout</Run> - Child members of the drill-down element will be displayed in the next column.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph />
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"><Run FontWeight="Bold">Normal Top Summary Layout</Run> - Child members of the drill-down element will be displayed in the next column with Top Positioned Summary.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph />
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"><Run FontWeight="Bold">Excel-Like Grid Layout</Run> - Child members of the drill-down element will be displayed in the same column.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph />
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"><Run FontWeight="Bold">No-Summaries Grid Layout</Run> - Members in the OlapGrid will be displayed without summaries.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph />
</ListItem>
</List>
